profile:
Whether you’re a do-it-yourselfer and need posts or deck footings, or you’re looking for a complete fence solution, GNFP is here to assist you!

The hardest part about building your own fence or deck is digging the post holes. Many new construction sites, as well as existing yards, are filled with rock and other debris, making post hole construction a real problem.

Don't pay to rent a dangerous gas auger and still end up struggling for days in the hot sun! Call on the experts at GNFP!
services:
Hole Digging,

Gas Line Hand Hole Digging,

Post Setting,

Fence Design,

Fence Construction, 
– Pre-Fabricated & Custom Fence Repairs,

Rotted Fence Post Replacement,

Fence Reconstruction,

Deck Piers & Footings,

Bollards

profile:
We Take Your House & Make It Your Home! 

From small exterior upgrades to complete home renovations, let our experienced, professional team make your next home project a breeze.
With our team's 20 combined years of renovation experience, we offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee on all our work. 

Our services include:

-Decks & Fences
-Kitchen Renovation/Remodeling
-Custom kitchen cabinets
-Custom washroom vanities
-Custom laundry room cabinets
-Custom countertops & backsplash
-Bathroom Renovation/Remodeling
-Basement Finishing
-Flooring (Ceramic tiles, Hardwood Flooring, Vinyl, Laminate)
-Stairs and Railings
-Plumbing Services
-Electrical Services
-Handyman services

Take the hassle out of your next home project and call the experts at Homes by Adam!

profile:
At Bolt Fences and Decks, Customer Service is our #1 Priority. We believe in value, honesty, integrity, and establishing both strong and reliable relationships with our Manufacturers and Customers, giving you the service with on time deliveries and using every avenue possible to satisfy your needs. Centrally located in the Niagara Region, we are able to service the entire Niagara Region. We believe in selling the finest products in the Industry with excellent prices.

Bolt Fences and Decks strive to bring you the absolute best service and even better prices. Bolt specializes in a variety of fencing products from Chain Link Fencing, Wood Fencing to Quality Decking and Railing. We also carry Gates, Dog Kennels, and more! Please take a look around and see what Bolt Fences and Decks has to offer you over our competition! At Bolt Fences and Decks, we can also make all of your dreams a reality. Our motto is "You Dream It - We'll Build It!"
specialities:
Value, Honesty, Integrity
Customer satisfaction is our #1 priority!
Quality Fence Products sourced from local suppliers in the Niagara Region
Every order is custom and complete

When you hire Bolt Fences and Decks, you'll benefit from

Personal commitment to your satisfaction from start to finish.
Fully Insured contractors ($5 million commercial liability insurance).
Fully Insured and trained workers (full WSIB coverage, no "day workers/cash under the table).
2 year warranty on all wood fencing.
